{"tid":85661,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「毒撚」用普通話講係咪啫係「單棍兒」？","createTime":"2017-01-18T13:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T14:56:51.000Z","uid":38539,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dea1d5fc104a5d04be35d410a4f9b3be597328e0","tid":85661,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"「毒」 與「獨」同音同意 有一個人の意味<br />\n「單」是一個的意思 ，買「單」雙亦是黃賭「毒」之一<br />\n「單」筆劃簡單，帶點正能量<br />\n<br />\n「撚」 因粗俗應改用比諭 = 一碌棍 <br />\n簡化後為「棍兒」，帶點傲氣<br />\n<br />\n∵ E=mc^{2}<br />\n<br />\n&there4;毒撚 = 單棍兒<br />\n<br />\n我正式宣佈「單棍兒」為粵語「毒撚」之普通話官方稱呼，走文雅青年路線！"},{"pid":"41e758d88fd2822f7903e441b995d2e891a0f843","tid":85661,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdjcGuSM3M4MRKBV4QRPsje3yNHcobiAo6viGE7qkG6sU?filename=NOF07.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOF07.gif&h=c77e97e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7df7165c40c272a5fe7fd1459e9c0ff585e83c0c","tid":85661,"uid":65615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:28:12.000Z","msg":"你唔比人係無棍兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a226b4ab41188f48a61225f3ba7662a3b5d06dbc","tid":85661,"uid":71093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"光棍兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f912a021c13ea51185397d6b9741fd434ed9de","tid":85661,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:35:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>光棍兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毒係暗屬性 光係光屬性 <br />\n有物理常識都知係相剋啲"},{"pid":"1defb27e709af3567541566a724bfadbaf1c9f15","tid":85661,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:36:00.000Z","msg":"你係單春兒"},{"pid":"613ddff04734472acd9df900f89f8691d2dd7c90","tid":85661,"uid":54602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"唔撚想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1367087ddca5b5c49a090f40b071790b1a7762","tid":85661,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔撚想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我志在分享"},{"pid":"7acc7f398607d723fa448d51482b2f97b77c1cc9","tid":85661,"uid":35393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:37:18.000Z","msg":"單身咪得，一係你用書面語<br />\n一係你用蝗語口語的屌絲，光棍<br />\n咩撚野單棍兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bb92f79605cabdcfde50a258cf38925ab99be5","tid":85661,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:45:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單身咪得，一係你用書面語<br />\n一係你用蝗語口語的屌絲，光棍<br />\n咩撚野單棍兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我認為「屌絲」 和「光棍」欠缺霸氣 是稱呼loser<br />\n但「單棍兒」參考「雙花紅棍」個朵撻出黎夠響"},{"pid":"b6d687d9ce09735eebb9ba0abd7e04a52f46f002","tid":85661,"uid":52859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:56:51.000Z","msg":"普你老母通話 垃圾語言 戇鳩"}]}